Name: Menzies
Description:
The Division of Menzies consists of:

  • Part of Manningham City Council,
  • Part of the Maroondah City Council, and
  • Part of the Nillumbik City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Retail, healthcare, education and training, manufacturing and various light industries.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of the Rt Hon. Sir Robert Gordon Menzies KT CH QC, 1894-1978. Menzies was Prime Minister of Australia (1939-41 and 1949-66) and a Member of the House of Representatives (1934-66).
DemographicRating: Outer Metropolitan - situated in capital cities and containing large areas of recent suburban expansion.
